Pumpkin Spice Pudding

30oz fresh pumpkin puree or 2x15oz cans of unsweetened pumpkin
3/4 c extra virgin coconut oil warmed to just liquid consistency
2/3 c maple syrup
1 tsp cinnamon
1/2 tsp ground ginger
1/4 tsp sea salt
1/4 tsp ground nutmeg
1/8 tsp ground cloves

In the jar of a blender, mix the pumpkin, oil, syrup, and spices. Blend on high for 1 min. Scrape down the sides and blend again for 1 min more. Pour the mixture into parfait glasses, cover with plastic wrap and refrigerate for at least 3 hrs.
